      "solution": "import sys\n\nW, H = map(int, input().split())\n# Handle edge cases where W or H is 1 (no hole)\nif W < 2 or H < 2:\n    print(W * H)\nelse:\n    # 2*w + 2*h - 4 accounts for corners to avoid double-counting\n    print(2 * W + 2 * H - 4)\n",
